{"tid":390136,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"許雅婷拍打戲周身瘀　陳婉衡解放","createTime":"2017-09-06T23:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T05:02:27.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62d494116a74aff68722d5c2d5cd4587b6ee2ca2","tid":390136,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170906/photo/bkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170906223333\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170906%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170906223333&h=16438557&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傷晒，陰功！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170906/photo/bkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170906223333\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170906%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170906223333&h=4e5d2c7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手又傷。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170906/photo/bkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170906223333\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170906%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20170906223333&h=cf784958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n腳又傷。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170906/photo/bkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001_04b.jpg?20170906223333\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170906%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20170906223333&h=fe607e2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n做女警。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170906/photo/bkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001_05b.jpg?20170906223333\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170906%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20170906223333&h=7f451b08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n勁呀！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170906/photo/bkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001_06b.jpg?20170906223333\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170906%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20170906223333&h=275bb220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳婉衡會同小方激吻。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170906/photo/bkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001_07b.jpg?20170906223333\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170906%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20170906223333&h=a67ed707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大合照。<br />\n<br />\n由錢國偉執導以「霸王花」為主題的網絡電影，起用36E咪神陳婉衡（Alycia）、少女標本成員許雅婷（Kabby）、功夫新星何佩珉及內地網紅孟孟主演，個個都打到飛起。首次拍打戲的Alycia及Kabby在開拍前接受武術訓練，未開工已經搞到周身傷，到正式拍攝時更是一個險跛、一個險聾！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Kabby疤痕就係戰績</strong><br />\n<br />\nKabby一雙美腿充滿瘀痕，認真慘情！她接受東網訪問時說：「到訓練時先發現之前玩打拳啲姿勢唔啱，要由頭練，已經搞到肌肉好痠痛！有一場戲要同春卷（王寶葆）對打，武指叫我哋唔好留手，結果我哋出真力真打，互相打到瘀晒！但最傷一場係我哋穿高跟鞋狂跑，跑咗好耐，對腳都冇晒知覺，我失足碌咗落樓梯撞親手踭，好在冇斷骨，但就損晒！（驚唔驚留疤？）身上有啲傷痕應該真係會留疤，冇辦法，呢啲係戰績！」不過，Kabby愈打愈上癮，希望朝打女路線進發。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Alycia騷36E導彈</strong><br />\n<br />\n至於同樣打到周身瘀傷的Alycia在拍攝一場槍戰戲時，由於忘記戴耳塞：「過咗幾日隻耳仔仲係聽到溫溫聲，有啲唔妥，如果再係咁就要睇醫生。」當然導演不會埋沒Alycia美好的身材，穿着Bikini Top騷36E上圍，更與客串的方力申上演一場水中錫錫戲。<br />\n<br />\n至於向來好打的何佩珉直言今次雖有瘀傷，但笑言不算太辛苦，最難忘的就是到兒童遊樂場拍打鬥場面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170906/bkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170906%2Fbkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001.html&d=%2BnNreoHSAT5xh0CxqRKFYwIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=8cc32474\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170906/bkn-20170906184109161-0906_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d6c1027805b0d612c9efaab2180e5374577d9bca","tid":390136,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:58:05.000Z","msg":"陳婉衡真係好撚樣衰呀 咪再比佢個樣出鏡啦"},{"pid":"dd895373590b403d43f16340aa8f0498b63f70f4","tid":390136,"uid":81569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:14:08.000Z","msg":"個kabby係咪整過容？<br />\n個鼻咁直既喂"},{"pid":"75739c69657aa7d5016c4a4f16967ab3b1ed115e","tid":390136,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:31:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個kabby係咪整過容？<br />\n個鼻咁直既喂</blockquote><br />\n未見過有人個鼻係咁"},{"pid":"6c6949586c6d8ba95adb787a399d61999854479a","tid":390136,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:16:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e062bfaa3dcecf785ac96ff10c05f65e2c59d33","tid":390136,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:56:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad72cea1b20e80cc01e1babd6a0232f3283aa7f5","tid":390136,"uid":7656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳婉衡真係好撚樣衰呀 咪再比佢個樣出鏡啦</blockquote><br />\n睇錯陳婉嫻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}